short_product_name: Hydra Aloe Vera Mousse nettoyante apaisante
incide_enDescription:
It is specially formulated for removing makeup from sensitive skin - so that it is no longer a source of discomfort - without soap or sulphate.
Enriched with pure organic aloe
        [more]
[more]

        vera juice with moisturizing properties, it cleans and removes the skin gently while preserving it from drying out.
With the presence of soothing bisabolol and soothing organic rose floral water.
        
[less]
